popularityCurve.label: this country in its unparalleled misfortune remains an enigma for students of its history in trying to shed light on the underlying causes of this age-old tragedy a specific-and always damaging-link has emerged between the seizure or maintenance of power and the practice of political murder be it individual or mass real or symbolic this long tradition of murder has doubtless created a collective consciousness that has little hope for a pacified political world
